  m_Text: "\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 GENERAL \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nWASD
    - Move\nMouse - Look\nLeft Shift - Sprint\nSpace - Jump\nLeft Ctrl - Descend
    / Sink\nEscape - Pause\n\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 INTERACTION \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nHold
    E - Interact / Equip suit\nHold Q - Drop held item\nF - Tug rope (signal surface)\nScroll
    Wheel / Numbers - Cycle inventory"
